<collectingCountry id="F337ECFEFFA7503B2A7A9F9FFE1DF81E" box="[365,501,1998,2024]" name="Cape Verde" pageId="53" pageNumber="54">Cape Verde</collectingCountry>
Islands, eastern North Atlantic Ocean (
<bibRefCitation id="EFB1D19FFFA7503B28D39F9FFB6EF81E" author="Chevreux, E." box="[964,1158,1998,2024]" pageId="53" pageNumber="54" pagination="1 - 8" refId="ref27482" refString="Chevreux, E. (1908) Diagnoses d'amphipodes nouveaux provenant des campagnes de la Princesse-Alice dans l'Atlantique nord. (suite). Bulletin De L'Institut Oceanographique, Monaco, 122, 1 - 8." type="journal article" year="1908">Chevreux, 1908</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
